chapters.title: Prologue:  Snow
chapters.info: Zaida din Parede Black Wing, p. 34 (24)—Sea Folk wavemistress. She is very commanding, and expects obedience from everyone. She is quite beautiful. Zaida is the Wavemistress of Clan Catelar and the ambassador to Rand from Nesta din Reas, Mistress of the Ships to the Sea Folk.
